also, it may be more clean/readable to have this scanning only if user didn't provide the contentType, so that we can avoid double subscription if not needed.
if (contentType != null) {
   return callAPI(data, contentType);
} else {
  return detectContentType(data)
     .flatmap(contentType -> {
         return callAPI(data, contentType);
     }); 
}

